---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Dolce Way | 22 Apps. One Developer. Zero Excuses.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Building in Public</p>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-heading leading-tight mb-6">
        22 Apps.<br />
        <span class="gradient-text">One Developer.</span><br />
        Zero Excuses.
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-subtle max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        I built a $4M company. Now I'm building an app empire.<br class="hidden md:block" />
        You're watching from day zero.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/apps"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all hover:scale-105"
        >
          See the Apps
        </a>
        <a
          href="/blog"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-surface-light hover:bg-border text-heading font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all border border-border hover:border-accent"
        >
          Read the Blog
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-y border-border bg-surface/50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="p-8">
          <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">22</p>
          <p class="text-subtle">Apps Built</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">$4M</p>
          <p class="text-subtle">Company Valuation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">1</p>
          <p class="text-subtle">Developer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Story Teaser -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-heading mb-8 text-center">
        The Story
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-body">
        <p>
          Most people have ideas.
        </p>
        <p>
          I have apps. 22 of them.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's not luck. That's a system.
        </p>
        <p class="text-subtle">
          I'm documenting the entire journey â€” the wins, the lessons, everything. Not to flex. To show you it's possible.
        </p>
        <p>
          You're early. Remember this moment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/about" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-light font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Read the full story
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Coming -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-surface/50 border-y border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">
        What You'll Find Here
      </h2>
      <p class="text-subtle mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Real content from someone who's doing it. Not theory. Results.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="gradient-border p-6 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">Build in Public</h3>
          <p class="text-subtle">What I shipped. What's next. No filter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gradient-border p-6 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">AI & Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-subtle">What I'm using to ship fast. The real stack.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gradient-border p-6 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">Mindset</h3>
          <p class="text-subtle">How winners think. The edge no one talks about.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gradient-border p-6 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">App Launches</h3>
          <p class="text-subtle">22 apps. Every launch documented.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-heading mb-6">
        You're Here Before the Numbers
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-subtle mb-10">
        22 apps. Ready to deploy. Ground floor access.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/connect"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all hover:scale-105"
        >
          Follow the Journey
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-muted text-sm">
        Your move.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
